&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;CONCEPT:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;When three quantities are in AP, the middle one is called as the arithmetic mean of the other two.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;FORMULAE USED:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;If a, b and c are three terms in AP&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;Then b = (a + c)/2&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;&quot;&gt;CALCULATION:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

