&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Given:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The sum of the first 151 terms of an AP whose first term and the third term are 175 and 185.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Formula used:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

