&lt;p&gt;So, difference(d) between the first and second term will be 10 &amp;divide; 2 = 5, a = 175 and n = 151( number of terms)&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Sn = &lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(\dfrac{151}{2}\)&lt;/span&gt; &amp;times; [2 &amp;times; 175 + (151 - 1) &amp;times; 5]&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;rArr; 75.5 &amp;times; [350 + 150 &amp;times; 5]&lt;/p&gt;

