&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;&quot;&gt;&amp;there4; The substance of zinc =&amp;nbsp;&lt;span class=&quot;math-tex&quot;&gt;\(225 \times \frac{5}{9}\)&lt;/span&gt;&amp;nbsp;= 125&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

